= IMG_LoadAnimation =

Load an animation from file 

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
IMG_Animation * IMG_LoadAnimation(const char *file);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''file'''
|file name
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns IMG Animation, or NULL on error.

== Version ==

This function is available since SDL_image 2.6.0.

